Hydrogen-bonded extended arrays of the [Re6(mu3-Se)8]2+ core-containing clusters. Site-differentiated solvated clusters of the general formula [Re(6)(mu(3)-Se)(8)(PEt(3))(n)(MeCN)(6)(-)(n)](SbF(6))(2) (n = 4, cis and trans n = 5) undergo ligand substitution reaction with isonicotinamide to afford the corresponding amide derivatives, [Re(6)(mu(3)-Se)(8)(PEt(3))(n)(isonicotinamide)(6)(-)(n)](2+) [1 (n = 5)